HEADWORD: Unlooked
<hw>Un*looked"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>un-</ets> not + <ets>looked</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not observed or
foreseen; unexpected; -- generally with <xex>for</xex>.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Unlooked</xex> success.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Denham.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>She comes <qex>unlooked</qex> for, if she comes at all.</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unlooked-for</ent>⟦br⟧
